Package: batchLLM
Type: Package
Title: batchLLM: Batch process LLM text completions using data frame rows
Version: 0.9.0
Author: Dylan Pieper
Maintainer: The package maintainer <dylanpieper@gmail.com>
Description: Batch process Large Language Model (LLM) text completions using data frame rows, with support for OpenAI's GPT, Anthropic's Claude, and Google's Gemini, along with features like local storage, metadata logging, delays for API rate limiting, and a Shiny App Addin.
